<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a35e5bb-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s8213"><num value="8213">§ 8213.</num><heading> Prohibition against implementation of regulatory authority by Federal agencies through partnerships</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any Partnership designated under this chapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a35e5bc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s8213/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> shall be for the sole purpose of promoting fish conservation; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a35e5bd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s8213/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> shall not be used to implement any regulatory authority of any Federal agency.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id7a35e5be-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/116/188/tII/s213">Pub. L. 116–188, title II, § 213</ref>, <date date="2020-10-30">Oct. 30, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/938">134 Stat. 938</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
